<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV63">
<l>naṉṟiruntu yōkanīti naṇṇuvārkaḷ cintaiyuṭ</l>
<l>ceṉṟiruntu tīviṉaikaḷ tīrttatēva tēvaṉē</l>
<l>kuṉṟirunta māṭanīṭu pāṭakattu mūrakattum</l>
<l>niṉṟiruntu veḵkaṇaikki ṭantateṉṉa nīrmaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Entering and remaining in the thoughts of people who undertake the path of yoga</l>
<l rend="indent">sitting properly,</l>
<l>O Lord of gods who ended the[ir] evil karman!</l>
<l>Such affability as [You] stand and sit in the large Pāṭakam and Ūrakam</l>
<l>with hill[-like] mansions, and recline in Veḵkaṇai?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
